  </svg>
  <h1>
    <div class="nl">Plant je site.<em>Laat hem groeien.</em></div>
    <div class="en">Plant your site.<em>Watch it grow.</em></div>
  </h1>
  <p class="sub">
    <span class="nl">WaldJS is een content-first webframework voor razendsnelle, statische websites. Schrijf <code style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.9em">.wald</code>-bestanden — deels frontmatter, deels HTML-template — en WaldJS compileert ze tot een statische site.</span>
    <span class="en">WaldJS is a content-first web framework for blazing-fast, static-first websites. Write <code style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.9em">.wald</code> files — part frontmatter, part HTML template — and WaldJS compiles them into a static site.</span>
  </p>
  <div class="cta">
    <a class="btn" href="#quickstart"><span class="nl">Plant je eerste bos 🌱</span><span class="en">Plant your first forest 🌱</span></a>
    <a class="btn ghost" href="https://github.com/Stefan-Espant/WaldJS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="nl">Bekijk op GitHub</span><span class="en">View on GitHub</span></a>
  </div>
  <div id="gh-stats" class="gh-stats">
    <span>⭐ <b id="gh-sterren">–</b> stars</span>
    <span>🍴 <b id="gh-forks">–</b> forks</span>
    <span><span class="nl">Open source</span><span class="en">Open source</span> · <b>MIT</b></span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal codeblok">
    <div class="titel"><span class="dot"></span>terminal</div>
    <pre><span id="term-tekst" class="term-cursor">$ </span>
<span id="term-uit" class="term-uit"></span></pre>
  </div>
  <p class="plant-hint"><span class="nl">🌱 Tip: klik ergens in het bos om een boom te planten</span><span class="en">🌱 Tip: click anywhere in the forest to plant a tree</span></p>
</header>

<!-- QUICK START -->
